'''Andraste''' is a character created specifically for [[The Lord of the Rings Online]]. She was the mistress of ''[[crebain]]'' that attacked [[Fredegar Bolger]].<ref>{{VGC|SAI}}, Chapter 7: "Horn-call of Buckland"</ref> She was slain in the [[Barrow-downs]] along with her crebain.<ref>{{VGC|SAI}}, Chapter 10: "Into the Barrow-downs"</ref>
